# sq-kalshi LIVE flavour credentials — copy to `.env` (same folder) and fill in.
# Preferred path is the OS keychain via `sciqnt kalshi setup`; this .env is the
# fallback. Generate the key in the Kalshi web UI (Account → API Keys). 0600, gitignored.
KALSHI_KEY_ID=
# Paste the full PEM block (multi-line). In a .env, wrap in quotes and use \n,
# or prefer the keychain path which handles multi-line natively.
KALSHI_PRIVATE_KEY=
